OL,3,GWales
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FA cloudier start with showery
OL,6,Frain pushing eastwards followed by the
OL,7,Frisk of thunderstorms in the east.
OL,8,FSome brighter spells developing in the
OL,9,Fwest through the afternoon. Lighter
OL,10,Fwinds than of late.
OL,11,
OL,12,CTonight:FShowers clearing to leave a
OL,13,Fdry start to the night with clear
OL,14,Fspells. Lower cloud then building in
OL,15,Ffrom the west, with some drizzle
OL,16,Fpossible over the hills.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
