OL,3,GWales
OL,4,
OL,5,CSaturday:FA rather cloudy start but
OL,6,Fsome bright spells will develop. A few
OL,7,Fshowers developing from lunchtime,
OL,8,Fwith a band of heavier rain arriving
OL,9,Ffrom the south later in the day.
OL,10,
OL,11,COutlook for Sunday to Tuesday:FShowers
OL,12,For longer spells of rain likely
OL,13,Fthrough Sunday and into Monday,
OL,14,Fpossibly thundery. A few showers still
OL,15,Fpossible Tuesday. Temperatures
OL,16,Fgenerally returning closer to average.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
